# Summary
Compass helps identify inflection metrics that predict user retention or conversion by analyzing correlations between user behaviors and desired outcomes, using metrics like proportion above threshold, positive predictive value (PPV), sensitivity, negative predictive value (NPV), and specificity to evaluate potential inflection points in the user journey.

